---
// TEST ISOLÉ — chrome rétro 98/2000.css (aucun impact sur l'OS réel).
// Ouvre http://localhost:4321/test-98 pour juger le rendu.
// Si tu valides, on branche le style sur Window.svelte ; sinon on jette ce fichier.
---
<html lang="fr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>2000 OS — test chrome 98/2000</title>
    <!-- 98.css : patterns Win98/2000 authentiques, ~10ko, via CDN -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/98.css" />
    <style>
      body { margin:0; background:#0a0b14 url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="8" height="8"><rect width="8" height="8" fill="%230a0b14"/><circle cx="1" cy="1" r="0.6" fill="%23161a2e"/></svg>'); font-family:sans-serif; padding:28px; display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:22px; align-items:flex-start; }
      h1 { color:#8fa0ff; font:600 13px monospace; width:100%; margin:0 0 4px; }
      p.sub { color:#5f6ba0; font:11px monospace; width:100%; margin:0 0 12px; }
      .window { width:300px; }
      .stack { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>2000 OS — test chrome 98/2000.css</h1>
    <p class="sub">Rendu des fenêtres/boutons rétro « prêts à l'emploi ». Test isolé — l'OS réel n'est pas touché.</p>

    <!-- Fenêtre classique -->
    <div class="window">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <div class="title-bar-text">VINCENT 2000 — night_drive.exe</div>
        <div class="title-bar-controls">
          <button aria-label="Minimize"></button>
          <button aria-label="Maximize"></button>
          <button aria-label="Close"></button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="window-body">
        <p>Tu roules sur la nationale. L'antenne grésille. Choisis une destination.</p>
        <div class="stack" style="margin-top:10px">
          <button>LA RIDE</button>
          <button>LE PMU</button>
          <button>LA RADIO PIRATE</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="status-bar">
        <p class="status-bar-field">03:14 AM</p>
        <p class="status-bar-field">88.6 FM</p>
        <p class="status-bar-field">CPU 2%</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Onglets + champs -->
    <div class="window">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <div class="title-bar-text">réglages_platine.cpl</div>
        <div class="title-bar-controls"><button aria-label="Close"></button></div>
      </div>
      <div class="window-body">
        <menu role="tablist">
          <li role="tab" aria-selected="true"><a href="#">Deck</a></li>
          <li role="tab"><a href="#">FX</a></li>
          <li role="tab"><a href="#">Radio</a></li>
        </menu>
        <div class="window" role="tabpanel">
          <div class="window-body">
            <div class="field-row"><label>BPM</label><input type="text" value="138" /></div>
            <div class="field-row">
              <input id="ukg" type="checkbox" checked /><label for="ukg">shuffle UKG</label>
            </div>
            <div class="field-row" style="margin-top:8px">
              <label for="crossfade">Crossfade</label>
              <input id="crossfade" type="range" min="0" max="100" value="42" />
            </div>
            <div class="field-row" style="margin-top:10px; justify-content:flex-end; gap:6px">
              <button>Annuler</button><button>OK</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Popup / dialogue -->
    <div class="window" style="width:250px">
      <div class="title-bar">
        <div class="title-bar-text">message</div>
        <div class="title-bar-controls"><button aria-label="Close"></button></div>
      </div>
      <div class="window-body">
        <p style="display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:center;">
          <span style="font-size:26px">📼</span>
          Insère le minidisc de 2019. Il y avait un truc dessus.
        </p>
        <div style="margin-top:10px; text-align:right"><button>OK</button></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
